{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/explore-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1737727572\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You\u2019re an explorer who answered a distress signal on this snowy peak.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Yet when you arrived, you found nothing\u2014no one in sight. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">To make matters worse, your helicopter crash-landed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/race-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1737727572\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Don\u2019t freak out, though\u2014you\u2019ve got a small but trusty snowmobile to rely on!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>-Carve through endless snow trails.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>-Launch snowballs like a pro to smash through obstacles.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>-Collect coins to upgrade your ride.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/Battle-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1737727572\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When you try to rest in your tent, you\u2019ll realize the mountain\u2019s nightlife is not your friend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Defend your camp from the chilling creatures of the snowfields, and find the Eternal Flame to protect your camp.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3404630/extras/fairy-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1737727572\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You may feel alone here, but\u2026 something\u2019s watching you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Do not resist the strange, ethereal energy 